verbose_text: CYP19 and P450scc protein showed similar expression patterns to that of LRH-1; the levels of CYP19 and P450scc protein in villi of the patients in URSA group were significantly lower than those in villi of patients in the control group (p < 0.05), but no significant difference was found in levels of CYP19 and P450scc protein in decidua between the URSA group and control group (p> 0.05).
